front.title: Someone Who Loves You
front.gametext: If Han was just lost and Leia is on table (or vice versa), place the just lost character on your Used Pile instead. OR If Leia is present at a site where Han is captive, release Han. OR Cancel a Force drain at a prison.
front.lore: Han's appreciation toward his mysterious liberator was rather quickly overcome.

cancels: A Force drain at a prison
